

Day 46 of #100DaysOfCode – Introduction to SIEM!

Today, I explored Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) on TryHackMe. SIEM plays a crucial role in cybersecurity by providing real-time analysis of security alerts generated by applications and network hardware.

✅ Learned the fundamentals of SIEM
✅ Understood its importance in network visibility and security monitoring
✅ Hands-on experience with log analysis and threat detection

Security professionals rely on SIEM to detect, investigate, and respond to cyber threats effectively. Excited to dive deeper into network visibility and incident response in the upcoming tasks!

